				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: songs for pulling?<a name="62731"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Sep 17 04 2:44 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Remember that you can turn around and move while starting to sing your song (took me a while to get used from playing casters). Indoors you can poke your head around a corner quickly then back off just long enough to get your song started, often times you will not agro mobs if you're quick. Invis is often a good song (if you don't have pets in your group near you) or clicky spell to have up. Highsun is a great song to have up for some pulls as well followed by a FM if you have it.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
