				<td colspan="2"><span>The songs I use to pull are, resist debuff (HoS/OoS), slow (not damage slow).
<br />

<br />
If mobs are known to have buffs or ds on them, I use cancel magic to pull.
<br />

<br />
Avoid using DoT to pull. If you ever get an add and need to Fade or mez, DoT messes it up.</span></td>
